### 1. Initial Entry Point

Display welcome message: "Hi, I'm Robin Hood - here to help you pay less and get more. Would you like to see where you can save money right now?"

- **User Response Options:**
    - "tell me how it works" ‚Üí Proceed to Step 2 (Area Selection)
    

### 2. Area Selection

Display message: "Have you always wanted to save money but didn't know where to start? We're here for you! We are a free, automatic system for checking eligibility for discounts and offers that help you save a lot - on interest, tax refunds and even bills, where to start?"

- **User selects:** "Tax refund" ‚Üí Proceed to Step 3 (Employment Status)

### 3. Employment Status Question

Display message: "Great! So I can check, I'll ask a few short questions (answer them briefly - less than a minute). Are you:"

1 ."I have been employed for the entire last 6 years" 

2 . "I was an employee for part of my life (referring to a period of years)"

1. "I am self-employed only" 

- **Options:**
- 1 ‚Üí Proceed to Step 4
- 2 ‚Üí Proceed to Step 4
- 3 ‚Üí Proceed to Step 11

### 4. Average Salary Question

Display message: "What is your average salary in recent years?"

- **Options:**
    - "Less than 8,000" ‚Üí Store value, proceed to Step 5
    - "8,000‚Äì18,000" ‚Üí Store value, proceed to Step 5
    - "More than 18,000" ‚Üí Store value, proceed to Step 5

### 5. Tax/Financial Criteria Check

Display message: "Does any of the following apply to you?"

- "I pay tax on my salary"
- "I have a pension/compensation/provident fund/training fund. I have paid tax in the last 6 years"
- "I have paid capital gains tax in the last 6 years"
- "I had capital market transactions that caused me a profit/loss in the last 6 years"
- **Options :**
    - If **YES** to any ‚Üí Proceed to Step 6 (Additional Eligibility Check)
    - If **NO** to all ‚Üí Proceed to Step 11 (No Savings Potential - Exit Message)

### 6. Additional Eligibility Check (First Level)

Display message: "Do you have children, academic studies, insurance payments, or grants you have received that could affect your eligibility for a refund?"

- **Options:**
    - "Yes" ‚Üí Proceed to Step 7 (Second Level Additional Check)
    - "No" ‚Üí Proceed to Step 7

### 7. Additional Eligibility Check (Second Level)

Display message: "Do you have children, academic studies, insurance payments, or grants you have received that could affect your eligibility for a refund?"

- **Options:**
    - "Yes" ‚Üí Proceed to Step 8 (Collect User Information)
    - "No" ‚Üí Proceed to Step 8

### 8. Collect User Information

Sequentially collect the following information:

1. **Full Name:** Text input field
2. **Phone Number:** Text/numeric input field
3. **ID Number:** Text/numeric input field

After collecting all information ‚Üí Proceed to Step 9

### 9. Savings Potential Assessment

Display message: "It looks like you have the potential to save a few hundred shekels a month. Want us to do a free in-depth check to make sure?"

- **Options:**
    - "Yes, check for me" ‚Üí **Send Tax Refund Template Message (NEW)** ‚Üí Then Step 10
    - "Take me back to the main menu to continue saving!" ‚Üí Return to Step 2 (Area Selection)
    
    ### **‚û°Ô∏è NEW MESSAGE (After ‚ÄòYes, check for me‚Äô is clicked)**
    
