### 10. Confirmation and Follow-up

Display message: "Thank you for choosing Robin Hood üèπ We will update you as soon as we find savings! Shall we continue to save in other areas?"

- **Option:**
    - "Take me back to the main menu to continue saving!" ‚Üí Return to Step 2 (Area Selection)

### 11. No Savings Potential - Exit Message

Display message: "Thank you for choosing Robin Hood üèπ It seems that you currently have no potential for savings in the area of tax refunds, so why not check out another area?"

- **Option:**
    - "Take me back to the main menu to continue saving!" ‚Üí Return to Step 2 (Area Selection)